{
  "texts": [
    "We ended the intermediate screening by discarding 313 publications and retaining 425 publications.",
    "For the final screening step, we screened the full papers to make sure they were within our scope and that they used ML to process scanpaths.",
    "We discarded 267 publications that were not passive gaze-based applications or for scanpath processing, and 81 publications that did not use ML for scanpath processing.",
    "We ended the screening phase with 77 publications for information extraction.",
    "We started the information extraction phase with 77 publications, which included 48 journal publications and 29 conference publications."
  ]
}